trailingComments.value: * * Optimization of {@link _concat} when x contains a single element. * Works even if x has dangling pointers x.next and x.prev. * * @param {Node} a - First node of list. * @param {Node} x - Node to be inserted at the end of list.
FROM a - b - c - d - a        x
TO a - b - c - d - x - a
